title: How To | No Makeup Look
description:
The trick to a natural ‘no makeup’ look, use a foundation with light coverage and opt for natural colors on your lips and eyes. 

Step 1: Start with a light foundation.

Step 2: Apply a highlight powder, like Neutrogena Healthy Skin® Blush in Luminous, all over face. Focusing most on the cheekbone area and eye creases.

Step 3: Use natural eye shadow tones on eyes.

Step 4: Finish look with a peachy-pink color on lips. 

Now you have a no makeup look for those natural kind of days. Follow our ‘How To’ series for more everyday makeup tips!
